platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In this gorgeous twist on the infinite runner, you guide an agile snowboarder down a never-ending mountain, pulling off backflips over icy chasms and grinding along rooftops in sleepy villages. Simple one-finger controls make it instantly accessible, but tackling each level’s trio of challenges requires deft reflexes. With its exquisitely rendered visuals, soothing music, and finely tuned gameplay, Alto’s Adventure is simultaneously serene and exciting.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: We're obsessed with nailing the perfect run while admiring the gorgeous scenery.
